### OWASP Top 10 Quick Check
- ✅ Parameterized queries (JOOQ type-safe)
- ✅ Response DTO (không Entity)
- ✅ JWT RS256, key ≥ 2048
- ✅ CSRF (JWT stateless → disabled)
- ✅ CSP headers
- ✅ File upload validation
- ✅ Error handler (no stack trace)
